{"tid":1933181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】世衛指全球已逾 20 萬病例　譚德塞：中國僅 60 日疫苗試驗屬驚人成就","createTime":"2020-03-19T06:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T11:16:14.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd41fc13afadca082a699c1693390b80964b050","tid":1933181,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Tedros-Adhanom-Ghebreyesus-1-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2FTedros-Adhanom-Ghebreyesus-1-1.jpg&h=1d895757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織﹝WHO﹞總幹事譚德塞在 18 日的記者會上表示，世衛目前合共收到全球接近 20 多萬宗武漢肺炎病例報告，至今約有 8,000 人因染病而死亡，呼籲所有國家採取一切辦法以阻止病毒的擴散，他亦特別強調中國在分享病毒基因序列 60 天後就已經進行第一次疫苗試驗，是一項令人難以置信的成就。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1197627465-e1584387104718.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2FGettyImages-1197627465-e1584387104718.jpg&h=e1794511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n譚德塞在是次記者會上提到目前中國在抗疫方面的工作，他指中國在分享病毒基因序列僅僅 60天後，就已經開始第一次疫苗試驗，無疑是一項令人難以置信的成就，並讚揚中國以及其他國家的研究人員。他呼籲所有國家採取一切辦法減慢病毒傳播速度，以拯救更多生命及為開發疫苗爭取更多的時間。<br />\n<br />\n他亦提到目前全球不少國家的醫療系統亦正面臨資源不足的情況，並建議相關人員可以在家照護部分病情較輕的患者，而世衛亦會在網上提供家庭護理的建議以及指引。他亦提到目前世衛與數十個國家亦開展一項研究工作，對一些未經測試的治療方法進行互相比較，以早日找出治病的方法。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：WHO<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/03/19/tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-praised-chinas-work-in-fighting-the-virus/life-tech/health/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F03%2F19%2Ftedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-praised-chinas-work-in-fighting-the-virus%2Flife-tech%2Fhealth%2F&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=a1e3383a\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/03/19/tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-praised-chinas-work-in-fighting-the-virus/life-tech/health/</a>"},{"pid":"4fbee2aa50265c4548e52cc47aad8d9b109e2014","tid":1933181,"uid":64191,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:54:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PGzZpR6CZ3M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPGzZpR6CZ3M&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=ecb4ca9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PGzZpR6CZ3M</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/54T0Eps.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F54T0Eps.jpg&h=cf4af1c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0de88144344da87b22503ba6ad1b15cafde5d903","tid":1933181,"uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:55:44.000Z","msg":"一日到黑都奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae19ed4c3d3d533af94e4a4619695926f848fab2","tid":1933181,"uid":15730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:57:11.000Z","msg":"又奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"607b129fe833ca6d73cf99db925679e8813f7acf","tid":1933181,"uid":280056,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:57:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母而家係支那搞到冚球鏟啊 仲想造神走數？ 啲左膠又係抵撚死"},{"pid":"5fb52f62cec1cc19828e2bc6b5fcce7404eedd17","tid":1933181,"uid":30215,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:57:27.000Z","msg":"自製病毒，自擕疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127eb789c2f38bcdfc65b221d9dea07e1697310a","tid":1933181,"uid":71583,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:00:09.000Z","msg":"係美國有疫苗先，又話係中國<br />\n病毒係中國，就話係美國<img s